{"title":"反“铁托观点”","authors":["纪初阳"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"反“铁托观点”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪初阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球跟着太阳转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能照一条路走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是共产主义的路；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是苏联的路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的“天文家”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着莫斯科，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“气象不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界都瞄着斯大林方向”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但铁托，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这禽兽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年伸出一支爪来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表示：要走第三条路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年光景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史给铁托的结论"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"证明："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反对地动律，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反共，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反苏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是叛徒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叛徒的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去＠帝国主义的屁股；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叛徒的路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山穷水尽！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}